{
  "name": "ListRows",
  "summary": "<p>每一个 <strong>ListRow</strong> 对象都代表表格中的一行。</p>\n<p>使用 <strong>ListObject</strong> 对象的 <strong>ListRows</strong> 属性可返回 <strong>ListRows</strong> 集合。</p>\n<p><b class=\"mainheaders\">示例</b></p><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*下例给第一张工作表的默认 ListObject 对象添加新行。由于未指定位置，因此在表格结束处添加一个新行。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> row = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListRows</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表的第一个 ListObject 对象中行的数量。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> listObj = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(listObj.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListRows</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
  "description": "<p>指定的 <strong>ListObject</strong> 对象中 <strong>ListRow</strong> 对象的集合。</p>\n",
  "category": "et",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "Application",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>如果不使用对象识别符，则该属性返回一个 <strong>Application</strong>对象，该对象表示 ET 应用程序。如果使用对象识别符，则该属性返回一个表示指定对象（可对一个 OLE 自动操作对象使用本属性来返回该对象的应用程序）创建者的 <strong>Application</strong> 对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code>*本示例显示一条有关创建 myObject 的应用程序的消息。*/\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n\t<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> myObject = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveWorkbook</span>\n\t<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (myObject.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value</span> == <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;ET&quot;</span>) {\n\t\t<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;This is an ET Application object.&quot;</span>)\n\t} <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n\t\t<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;This is not an ET Application object.&quot;</span>)\n\t}\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "Application",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Count",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong>Integer</strong> 值，它代表集合中对象的数量。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表上包含 C2 单元格的列表中行的数量。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> listObj = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C2&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListObject</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(listObj.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListRows</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（int4 精度）",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Creator",
      "summary": "<p>如果该对象是在 ET 中创建的，则此属性返回字符串 XCEL，它等同于十六进制的数字 5843454C。<strong>Creator</strong> 属性是为 Macintosh 上的 ET 设计的，在 Macintosh 上，每个应用程序都具有一个四字符的创建者代码。例如，ET 的创建者代码为 XCEL。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 32 位整数，该整数指示在其中创建此对象的应用程序。只读 <strong>Long</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
      "type": "XlCreator",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Parent",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回指定对象的父对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
      "type": "Object",
      "readonly": true
    }
  ],
  "functions": [
    {
      "name": "Add",
      "summary": "<p>如果不指定 <em>Position</em>，新行将添加到底部。如果不指定 <em>AlwaysInsert</em>，表格下面的单元格将下移一行（与指定 <strong>True</strong> 的作用相同）。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>向指定的 <strong>ListObject</strong>所代表的表格中添加新行。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*以下示例向工作簿的第一张工作表中的默认 ListObject 对象添加新行。由于未指定位置，新行将添加到列表的底部。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> row = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListRows</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*下例给活动工作表的第一个 ListObject 对象添加一个新行，并加到列表中现有行的第四个位置。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListRows</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">4</span>, <span class=\"hljs-literal\">false</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [
        {
          "name": "Position",
          "type": "any",
          "description": "<p>Integer 类型。指定新行的相对位置。</p>\n",
          "optional": true
        },
        {
          "name": "AlwaysInsert",
          "type": "any",
          "description": "<p>Boolean。指定在插入新行时，是否始终移动表格中最后一行下面的单元格中的数据，而不考虑表格下面的行是否为空行。如果为 True，则表格下面的单元格将下移一行。如果为 False，并且表格下面的行为空行，则表格将扩展以占用该空行而不移动它下面的单元格；但如果表格下面的行包含数据，则在插入新行时，这些单元格将下移。</p>\n",
          "optional": true
        }
      ],
      "returns": "<p>一个代表新行的 ListRow 对象。</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "name": "Item",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>从集合中返回一个对象。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示第一张工作表的第一个 ListObject 对象中第一行的索引。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> listObj = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(listObj.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListRows</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Index</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将活动工作表的第一个 ListObject 对象的第三行删除。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> listObj = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    listObj.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListRows</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Delete</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [
        {
          "name": "Index",
          "type": "any",
          "description": "<p>对象的名称或索引号。</p>\n",
          "optional": false
        }
      ],
      "returns": "ListRow"
    }
  ]
}